Sentencas: In this paper, a new method is proposed to identify solid oxide fuel cell using extreme learning machine-Hammerstein model (ELM-Hammerstein).
Titulo: Application of ELM-Hammerstein model to the identification of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The ELM-Hammerstein model consists of a static ELM neural network followed by a linear dynamic subsystem.
Titulo: Application of ELM-Hammerstein model to the identification of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: First, the structure of ELM-Hammerstein model is determined by Lipschitz quotient criterion from input-output data.
Titulo: Application of ELM-Hammerstein model to the identification of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Then, a generalized ELM algorithm is proposed to estimate the parameters of ELM-Hammerstein model, including the parameters of linear dynamic part and the output weights of ELM.
Titulo: Application of ELM-Hammerstein model to the identification of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The proposed method can obtain accurate identification results and its computation is more efficient.
Titulo: Application of ELM-Hammerstein model to the identification of solid oxide fuel cells
